data.description: Living square feet is 1951 as per Miami Dade County.  Miami Springs gem features 4 bedroom, 2 bathrooms, and brand-new updates and finishes throughout. The curb appeal speaks for itself, but some of the things you can't see right away are the new flat roof as of 11/2023, new gas water heater, new electrical panel, new split unit for the laundry room, and more. total 2,324 sq ft, and a 7,680 sq ft lot. One of the best priced homes in all of Miami Springs. This will not last.
